==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oleo oil
<hw>O`le*o oil</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>An oil expressed from certain
animal fats (esp. beef suet), the greater portion of the solid fat, or
stearin, being left behind. It is mixture of olein, palmitin, and a
little stearin.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oleoptene</ent>⟦br⟧
